text:
for getting tags in use within a blog you can reference this snippet
```{% if content.topic_list %}
    &lt;p id="HubSpot-topic_data"&gt; Topics:
        {% for topic in content.topic_list %}
            &lt;a class="topic-link" href="{{ blog_tag_url(group.id, topic.slug) }}"&gt;{{ topic.name }}&lt;/a&gt;{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
    &lt;/p&gt;
{% endif %}```
from here: <https://designers.HubSpot.com/docs/hubl/blog-content-markup>
